\title{What is a Proof Tactic}
\date{2026-05-16}
\taxon{Note}

\p{A proof tactic acts as a "step" in a proof built with an interactive theorem prover.}

\p{To understand a tactic, one must understand the difference between forward and backward reasoning as it pertains to proof assistants.}

